{"tid":2324915,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警無交代凍戶理據 梁繼昌轟損港聲譽","createTime":"2020-12-14T09:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T09:45:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9d68209f80a35c9d0c7449201173496e3137e16f","tid":2324915,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:40:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201214/2GT36AO4KRBXFLIL7NXDG22CBE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201214%2F2GT36AO4KRBXFLIL7NXDG22CBE%2F&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725N5VMZmAwfp0CD4JwUII9h4%3D&h=07be8ce1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201214%2F2GT36AO4KRBXFLIL7NXDG22CBE%2F&h=c4870c6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201214/2GT36AO4KRBXFLIL7NXDG22CBE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警無交代凍戶理據 梁繼昌轟損港聲譽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hKvFP5XLPAlYDnXIxVdXkRqbqxg=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/72HFAG2R6RHQZHZVELTFMCBH4A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhKvFP5XLPAlYDnXIxVdXkRqbqxg%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F72HFAG2R6RHQZHZVELTFMCBH4A.jpg&h=f2194215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁繼昌<br />\n<br />\n【本報評】早前立法會前議員許智峯與其家人，以及好鄰舍北區教會銀行戶口先後遭凍結，警方指兩案涉眾籌及洗黑錢，令社會關注眾籌活動受打壓。前會計界立法會議員梁繼昌質疑，警方簡單指事涉洗黑錢，卻沒有交代案件涉及哪條法例，做法不合理，會對香港作為金融中心運作及聲譽產生很大影響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/luJ0i5lnEibVIvkFNSafx8zOwJI=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A2YRY2T2OZFF5NMU6BZO6DDNF4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FluJ0i5lnEibVIvkFNSafx8zOwJI%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA2YRY2T2OZFF5NMU6BZO6DDNF4.jpg&h=ea6df00b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■早前警方凍結好鄰舍教會戶口後，在其辦公室撿走一批證物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KHyASwcTTKllozhVXYY0AGvVRh4=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5R25ROJAGRFC5KZ6RKUY24H47U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKHyASwcTTKllozhVXYY0AGvVRh4%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5R25ROJAGRFC5KZ6RKUY24H47U.jpg&h=6a16913a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周浩鼎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提醒眾籌注意三問題<br />\n<br />\n港台城市論壇昨討論眾籌問題，對於警方指眾籌或涉洗黑錢而凍結相關人士銀行戶口，梁繼昌認為較好做法是警方向法庭申請凍結令。對於警方強調要求銀行凍結許智峯相關戶口，是因懷疑他挪用眾籌所得部份款項、涉犯洗黑錢罪，梁質疑警方未有清楚說明案件涉及哪條法例，認為會對香港作為金融中心運作及聲譽產生很大影響。<br />\n<br />\n曾任職銀行的民主黨區議員盧俊宇認為，用普通戶口進行眾籌會有較大風險；最理想是開設獨立戶口，用作收款，並向銀行作出指示，眾籌達標後凍結收款功能。不過梁繼昌認為在銀行開戶不易，若有要事眾籌，或遠水不能救近火，強調由有公共信託管理經驗的律師及會計師協助，並整存紀錄是最重要。梁繼昌又提醒眾籌有三大問題要注意，包括眾籌目的，「眾籌買軍火梗係衰梗」；其次是眾籌來源要清楚；最後是管理，發起人亦即信託人要向公眾負責，用途必須與眾籌目的一致。<br />\n<br />\n會計師公會前副會長林。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"d3d20d9f647b2f34f0ce2077e3debaae2804fe02","tid":2324915,"uid":160373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:41:32.000Z","msg":"私有產權喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fcd7ba6bf337d516f6093c49576f6b8a5a4f02","tid":2324915,"uid":61447,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:45:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">前</span></span>會計界立法會議員梁繼昌"}]}